31:29.000 --> 31:32.000
the capitalist pricing problem, as I define it,

31:32.000 --> 31:34.000
really has to do in terms of...

31:34.000 --> 31:37.000
is a way of thinking about pricing systems

31:37.000 --> 31:42.000
in relationship to negative externalities.

31:42.000 --> 31:46.000
And in a larger sense, I see this as part of the question

31:46.000 --> 31:49.000
of the more important question of

31:49.000 --> 31:54.000
