59:00.000 --> 59:03.000
that the transformations in the mode of production,

59:03.000 --> 59:06.000
and I would include these shifts in economic ontology

59:06.000 --> 59:08.000
as a shift in the mode of production,

59:08.000 --> 59:14.000
ultimately transforms the culture in its image more so.

59:14.000 --> 59:16.000
You can't have one without the other,

